---
title: Indian Beef Kofta Curry with Basmati Rice & Mint
description: Rich, creamy and aromatic – this dish has all the elements of your favourite Indian curry – with a twist! Tender beef koftas add mouth-watering flavour and texture to this hearty bowl. Sitting on a bed of fluffy basmati rice, it comes together fast for a meal that everyone will love!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/indian-beef-kofta-curry-5b1c651a.jpg
